Sylphy's contribution
is the most relevant.

223
00:11:59,561 --> 00:12:01,927
[TRIKEN]
You're right, that's kind of an
unexpected twist, isn't it?

224
00:12:02,027 --> 00:12:06,094
[ISUZU]
I think we need to ask for other
people's opinions now.

225
00:12:06,194 --> 00:12:07,827
What about the
most important person?

226
00:12:07,927 --> 00:12:09,161
Talk to her next.

227
00:12:09,261 --> 00:12:12,394
[TRIKEN]
The most important person,
you say?

228
00:12:14,627 --> 00:12:17,594
[LATIFAH]
Yes...? Did you need me?

229
00:12:26,972 --> 00:12:29,805
[LATIFAH]
A promotional video?
I'm sorry...

230
00:12:29,905 --> 00:12:32,605
but I wouldn't know how to help
with something like that.

231
00:12:32,705 --> 00:12:34,105
[TRIKEN]
Anything will be helpful...

232
00:12:34,205 --> 00:12:35,872
Perhaps you could tell me
what sort of things

233
00:12:35,972 --> 00:12:38,105
you'd like the video
to be about.

234
00:12:38,205 --> 00:12:39,505
[LATIFAH]
Hmm...

235
00:12:39,605 --> 00:12:40,839
[LATIFAH]
Oh I know...!

236
00:12:40,939 --> 00:12:43,005
This is the
perfect opportunity...!

237
00:12:43,105 --> 00:12:44,705
Why don't you feature
the park employees

238
00:12:44,805 --> 00:12:46,072
who work behind the scenes

239
00:12:46,172 --> 00:12:48,805
so they can have a chance
to shine for a change?

240
00:12:50,905 --> 00:12:52,705
[MOLE A]
(carrying)

241
00:12:52,805 --> 00:12:53,805
[MOLE B]
(carrying)

242
00:12:53,905 --> 00:12:55,505
[TARAMO]
A promo? Well I'll be!

243
00:12:55,605 --> 00:12:58,039
Maybe this is what
you're looking for.

244
00:12:58,139 --> 00:12:59,739
[TRIKEN]
I see...

245
00:13:00,739 --> 00:13:02,472
[NICK]
You're making a video?

246
00:13:02,572 --> 00:13:05,439
[TRIKEN]
That's right...! Do you think I
could get a shot of you cooking?

247
00:13:05,539 --> 00:13:08,672
[NICK]
No thanks... too much effort.

248
00:13:08,772 --> 00:13:10,239
[TRIKEN]
Excuse me, Mr. Wrench‐

249
00:13:10,339 --> 00:13:12,972
