Dammit all, can'tcha see
I'm busy?!

250
00:13:13,072 --> 00:13:15,439
[OKURO]
Huh? You're filming again?

251
00:13:15,539 --> 00:13:19,772
Yes. But this time
I want to focus on the
security force as a whole.

252
00:13:19,872 --> 00:13:22,105
Perhaps I'll get some footage
of you working the gate

253
