things of that nature.

254
00:13:25,805 --> 00:13:27,672
[OKURO]
Oh really? That sounds good.

255
00:13:27,772 --> 00:13:30,172
[ASHE]
I'm sorry, I'm not sure how to
make accounting

256
00:13:30,272 --> 00:13:32,472
