So what should I do?

257
00:13:32,572 --> 00:13:36,272
[TRIKEN]
That's alright, Miss Ashe,
it doesn't have to be your job;

258
00:13:36,372 --> 00:13:38,139
it could be something you do
on your days off.

259
00:13:38,239 --> 00:13:40,972
