interesting...

262
00:13:48,439 --> 00:13:49,939
from back in my school days.

263
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:52,872
[TRIKEN]
Ah... and what is that?

264
00:13:52,972 --> 00:13:55,305
[RUBRUM]
Footage of my club activities.

265
00:13:56,839 --> 00:13:58,805
[DORNELL]
You need help with a promo?

266
00:13:58,905 --> 00:14:00,839
[TRIKEN]
Right, I'm looking
for suggestions

267
00:14:00,939 --> 00:14:03,005
from as many park employees
as possible.

268
00:14:03,105 --> 00:14:06,805
I'd love to come up
with something unique
that makes a big impact.

269
00:14:06,905 --> 00:14:09,205
[DORNELL]
Wouldn't you know it
I have just the thing.

270
00:14:09,305 --> 00:14:13,305
It's something I made
with a group of
like‐minded individuals.

271
00:14:14,539 --> 00:14:15,905
[JACK]
If you gimme some time...

272
00:14:16,005 --> 00:14:20,372
I'll go on a wild west adventure
and film it for ya.

273
00:14:20,472 --> 00:14:22,972
[GENJURO]
I think this noble endeavor
could greatly benefit

274
00:14:23,072 --> 00:14:24,639
from the spirit of the samurai!

275
00:14:24,739 --> 00:14:27,872
