What about a hard‐hitting drama

278
00:14:31,239 --> 00:14:32,705
about saving the earth?

279
00:14:33,905 --> 00:14:37,705
[TRIKEN]
Hello... Mr. Codain?
What do you think?

280
00:14:37,805 --> 00:14:42,805
[TRIKEN]
Do you ever talk at all?
Ah! What's that?

281
00:14:55,072 --> 00:14:56,539
Okay, today
I'm gonna demonstrate

282
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:58,372
the proper method
for slicing meat...

283
00:14:58,472 --> 00:15:01,372
First you hold the knife
just like this and then...

284
00:15:01,872 --> 00:15:04,039
I SAID BEAT IT!

285
00:15:05,005 --> 00:15:05,939
[PRO WRESTLER/OKURO]
(lockup)

286
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:07,072
[OKURO]
(punched)(effort)

287
00:15:07,172 --> 00:15:08,039
[PRO WRESTLER]
(punch)(splutter)

288
00:15:17,839 --> 00:15:19,039
[GUY A]
That's awesome!

289
00:15:19,139 --> 00:15:21,472
[DORNELL]
I feel so inspired now!

290
00:15:21,572 --> 00:15:22,872
[GUY B]
Totally worth the trip!

291
00:15:22,972 --> 00:15:25,439
[GUY C]
Look this way, guys,
you're on video!

292
00:15:25,539 --> 00:15:29,205
<deer chaser clunk>

293
00:15:43,372 --> 00:15:44,805
[JACK]
Hyahhhh!

294
00:15:44,905 --> 00:15:46,805
[JACK]
(kicked off)

295
00:15:52,005 --> 00:15:53,539
[GENJURO]
(inhale) In my final hour...

296
00:15:53,639 --> 00:15:56,605
my humble heart
is cleansed of all regret.

297
00:15:56,705 --> 00:15:59,439
For I know I sacrifice my life

298
00:15:59,539 --> 00:16:02,072
for the sake of
countless others.

299
00:16:02,172 --> 00:16:03,205
(seppuku grunt)

300
00:16:26,905 --> 00:16:30,105
[ISUZU]
I didn't understand that...
but I think it works.

301
00:16:30,205 --> 00:16:32,539
[TRIKEN]
What?! THIS is what we want?

302
00:16:32,639 --> 00:16:34,772
[ISUZU]
I'm curious about Ashe's part...

303
00:16:34,872 --> 00:16:36,205
What on earth was she doing?

304
00:16:36,305 --> 00:16:39,105
It's a competitive sport
known as extreme ironing...

305
00:16:39,205 --> 00:16:42,305
Apparently you're supposed to
iron clothes in bizarre places.

306
00:16:42,405 --> 00:16:44,705
Well, I suppose we all have
our hobbies, don't we?

307
00:16:44,805 --> 00:16:47,972
[ISUZU]
I didn't really understand
the part with Dornell
visiting the dam either.

308
00:16:48,072 --> 00:16:52,970
[TRIKEN]
I wasn't aware of it before,
but it turns out there's quite
a fan base for dams.

309
00:16:54,777 --> 00:16:58,510
[ISUZU]
Well alright then...
Each part of the video does seem
special in its own way,

310
00:16:58,610 --> 00:17:00,810
so it covers a wide range
of interests.

311
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:02,944
[TRIKEN]
Indeed... and I believe
we have enough footage

312
00:17:03,044 --> 00:17:05,277
to work with at this point,
wouldn't you agree?

313
00:17:05,377 --> 00:17:07,310
[ISUZU]
Oh I don't think
I'd say that yet...

314
00:17:07,410 --> 00:17:09,610
The next step is to hear
the opinion of someone

315
00:17:09,710 --> 00:17:11,677
who's closer to
a visitor's viewpoint.

316
00:17:11,777 --> 00:17:13,410
[TRIKEN]
And where are we
going to get that?

317
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:17,210
[ISUZU]
Talk to those three girls
we hired recently.

318
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:19,277
[BIINO]
I'd say it needs more
blood and guts!

319
00:17:19,377 --> 00:17:20,777
[TRIKEN]
Why blood and guts?!

320
00:17:20,877 --> 00:17:22,944
[BIINO]
You know...! Everybody likes
to watch things

321
00:17:23,044 --> 00:17:24,544
that creep them out, don't they?

322
00:17:24,644 --> 00:17:27,677
So just throw in a bit
of violence and it'll be
a masterpiece.

323
00:17:27,777 --> 00:17:31,544
Trust me on this one...
It's gonna be a big hit
with the visitors.

324
00:17:31,644 --> 00:17:35,310
[TRIKEN]
Well... i‐if you're
sure about it...

325
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:39,844
[SHIINA]
I... I think the video
looks fonderwul!

326
00:17:39,944 --> 00:17:41,877
N‐no wait I mean... W‐wonderful!

327
00:17:41,977 --> 00:17:44,010
[TRIKEN]
Is that how you honestly feel?

328
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:47,977
[SHIINA]
W‐well... maybe...
you uh... (nervous)

329
00:17:48,077 --> 00:17:50,077
Actually nevermind,
don't worry about it!

330
00:17:50,177 --> 00:17:50,977
[TRIKEN]
Hmmm...

331
00:17:51,644 --> 00:17:52,910
[EIKO]
Wow Triken...

332
00:17:53,010 --> 00:17:54,777
I think you've done
a beautiful job with this.

333
00:17:54,877 --> 00:17:56,444
[TRIKEN]
You think it's beautiful?

334
00:17:56,544 --> 00:17:58,744
[EIKO]
Of course...! Although...

335
00:17:58,844 --> 00:18:01,744
if you wouldn't mind me stating
my own personal opinion...

336
00:18:01,844 --> 00:18:03,310
I just can't help
but feel that it's

337
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:06,010
lacking a certain emotional
quality in its current state.

338
00:18:06,110 --> 00:18:08,910
[TRIKEN]
Emotional?
Do you have an example?

339
00:18:09,010 --> 00:18:12,310
[EIKO]
You see... I happen to be quite
interested in horses.

340
00:18:12,410 --> 00:18:16,077
They've been a hobby of mine
since I was a girl, actually.

341
00:18:16,177 --> 00:18:16,944
[TRIKEN]
Huh.

342
00:18:17,044 --> 00:18:18,310
[EIKO]
And not too long ago,

343
00:18:18,410 --> 00:18:20,277
I was lucky enough
to have a chance to witness

344
00:18:20,377 --> 00:18:21,677
a mother horse giving birth.

345
00:18:21,777 --> 00:18:23,710
It was a horse that's been
very special to me

346
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:25,010
since I was in high school...

347
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:27,010
Her name's Kikuno Scepter,
isn't that sweet?

348
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,577
[TRIKEN]
That's an interesting name...

349
00:18:28,677 --> 00:18:30,810
[EIKO]
The delivery was
extremely difficult...

350
00:18:30,910 --> 00:18:33,677
but now she's a proud mother!

351
00:18:33,777 --> 00:18:34,810
In all my life...

352
00:18:34,910 --> 00:18:36,977
I've never been so moved!

353
00:18:37,077 --> 00:18:45,210
[TRIKEN]
(extended amazement)
Finished!

354
00:18:45,310 --> 00:18:47,144
[TRIKEN]
It's amazing!

355
00:19:07,010 --> 00:19:08,710
[GAL A/GAL B]
(laughing)

356
00:19:09,310 --> 00:19:10,244
[GIRL A]
(giggle)

357
00:19:10,344 --> 00:19:11,310
[BOY B]
(giggle)

358
00:19:12,677 --> 00:19:14,777
[MODEL A]
Ooh...

359
00:19:15,710 --> 00:19:17,377
[MODEL B]
(sexy giggle)

360
00:19:18,644 --> 00:19:19,710
[MODEL F]
Yum...

