Moff.

368
00:19:32,177 --> 00:19:33,677
[MACARON]
Ron!

369
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:36,877
[TIRAMY]
Heheh...

370
00:19:39,677 --> 00:19:40,744
[GUY A]
That's awesome!

371
00:19:40,844 --> 00:19:43,044
[DORNELL]
I feel so inspired now!

372
00:19:43,144 --> 00:19:44,710
[GUY B]
Totally worth the trip!

373
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:46,244
[GUY C]
Look this way guys‐

374
00:19:47,777 --> 00:19:49,210
[JACK]
Hyahhh!

375
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,077
[GENJURO]
(seppuku grunt)

376
00:19:50,177 --> 00:19:51,344
[MODEL F]
Yum...

377
00:19:57,377 --> 00:19:59,877
[MUSE]
(snooze)

378
00:20:02,177 --> 00:20:05,110
[CROWD]
(synchronized headbanging)

379
00:20:05,210 --> 00:20:07,844
First you hold the knife
just like this and then...

380
00:20:07,944 --> 00:20:09,710
[WRENCH]
I SAID BEAT IT!

381
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:11,410
[JACK]
(kicked off)

382
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,744
[MODEL F]
Yum...

