<deer chaser>

384
00:20:14,377 --> 00:20:16,277
<bush warbler>

385
00:20:38,271 --> 00:20:43,171
[WANIPEE]
(slo‐mo death)

386
00:20:43,271 --> 00:20:45,304
[GUY D]
