Kikuno won't make it!

388
00:20:48,004 --> 00:20:48,971
[GUY E]
Let's pull it out!

389
00:20:49,071 --> 00:20:50,138
[GUY D]
It's a tough angle,

390
00:20:50,238 --> 00:20:51,238
but I think we're gonna have to!

391
00:20:51,338 --> 00:20:53,038
[GUY D] Get ready!
[GUY E] Right!

392
00:20:53,138 --> 00:20:54,204
[GUY D]
Hang in there, Kikuno!

393
00:20:54,304 --> 00:20:55,504
[GUY E]
Kikuno, push!

394
00:20:56,438 --> 00:20:57,404
[GUY D]
Come on out, we're almost there!

395
00:20:57,504 --> 00:20:59,071
[GUY E]
