396
00:20:59,171 --> 00:21:10,004
[GUY D/GUY E]
(heavy breathing,
into happy laughter)

397
00:21:11,871 --> 00:21:16,271
<Seiya speechless>

398
00:21:16,371 --> 00:21:17,838
[SEIYA]
What the hell did you DO?!

399
00:21:17,938 --> 00:21:21,004
Ah yes, I knew I'd get a big
reaction from you, Mr. Kanie.

400
00:21:21,104 --> 00:21:24,204
