You were supposed to be
supervising this project!

401
00:21:24,304 --> 00:21:25,138
What were you doing?!

402
00:21:25,238 --> 00:21:27,638
[ISUZU]
I'm so moved!

403
00:21:27,738 --> 00:21:28,538
What?!

404
00:21:28,638 --> 00:21:30,471
[ISUZU]
It's a touching story...

405
00:21:30,571 --> 00:21:32,938
of dreams coming true...

406
00:21:33,038 --> 00:21:35,038
What's not to like about it?

407
00:21:35,138 --> 00:21:37,204
<stammering>

408
00:21:37,304 --> 00:21:38,871
[SEIYA]
Everything!

409
00:21:40,504 --> 00:21:44,671
(cast complaining)

410
00:21:47,571 --> 00:21:49,004
[MOFFLE]
Moff, not enough action.

411
00:21:49,104 --> 00:21:50,871
[DORNELL]
Yeah and what happened
to the dam?

412
00:21:50,971 --> 00:21:54,004
[MACARON]
Nah, the real problem
is the music selection‐ron.

413
00:21:54,104 --> 00:21:56,471
[TARAMO]
I thought you were gonna
use our footage.

414
00:21:56,571 --> 00:21:59,271
[TIRAMY]
Where's my collection of
sexy pictures‐mii?

415
00:21:59,371 --> 00:22:03,104
[WANIPEE]
I don't understand why
nobody bothered asking ME
for an idea.

416
00:22:03,204 --> 00:22:04,438
[SEIYA]
Quit complaining...!

417
00:22:04,538 --> 00:22:06,038
We can't use that one.

418
00:22:07,171 --> 00:22:08,904
[TRIKEN]
Actually Mr. Kanie,

419
00:22:09,004 --> 00:22:12,004
