to upload the other video
to the internet as well.

420
00:22:12,104 --> 00:22:12,904
You what?!

421
00:22:13,004 --> 00:22:15,071
And it's going viral.

422
00:22:18,271 --> 00:22:20,038
No way!

423
00:23:50,071 --> 00:23:53,504
[SEIYA/ISUZU]
Time for the
attractions spotlight.

424
00:23:53,604 --> 00:23:55,704
[ISUZU]
Today's feature is Whip Antique.

425
00:23:55,804 --> 00:23:59,604
[SEIYA]
Wait, this was the last episode.
And why does it say "no image"?

426
00:23:59,704 --> 00:24:00,871
ISUZU
Don't worry about it.

427
00:24:00,971 --> 00:24:03,671
Whip Antique.
Where fantasies come true.

428
00:24:03,771 --> 00:24:05,571
Everybody loves Whip Antique.

429
00:24:05,671 --> 00:24:07,004
Did you need to repeat that?

430
00:24:07,104 --> 00:24:08,771
Come on down to Whip Antique.

431
00:24:08,871 --> 00:24:11,604
[SEIYA]
I get it. This is some kind of
advertisement.

432
00:24:11,704 --> 00:24:14,138
[ISUZU]
Remember, it's Whip Antique.

433
00:24:14,238 --> 00:24:16,704
I'm not sure what kind of shop
it is, or what they sell.

434
00:24:16,804 --> 00:24:18,804
[SEIYA]
Don't you think
that's important?!

